    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Extend adjectives on the board:</span> If QUICK, SHARP, or BOLD is already played, adding -LY creates a bingo-length word and scores all letters plus premium squares the extension crosses. This is one of the easiest extensions in the game.</p>
